dct_title_s: Kaart van de twee platte warelds bollen waar in aangetoond word alt geen tot heden is ondekt na de Nieuste kaarten getekent
dct_description_sm: Jacobus Keizer; Jan de Lat; O. Lindeman fecit.
California shown as a labeled island with place names and an indented northern coast. It is touching the mainland in the center.
Title in cartouche at top between hemispheres. Includes charts at top right and left.
